<A>__{the pakistani exits the adult bookstore.}
<C>__{pakistani}
<D>__{what is it?! what do you see?!}
<A>__{when adam looks down to answer the man he sees the "adult bookstore" sign.}
<C>__{adam}
<D>__{oh, no!}
